62
00:03:19,574 --> 00:03:21,034
Excuse me. There's
a boy who needs help.

63
00:03:21,118 --> 00:03:22,786
{\an8}MAN: Go tell your parents.
Please, there's something wrong.

64
00:03:22,869 --> 00:03:25,038
Go tell your parents!
(PANTING)

65
00:03:27,457 --> 00:03:29,084
Sir, please. There's
somebody who needs help.

66
00:03:29,167 --> 00:03:30,210
Not right now.
Please.

67
00:03:30,293 --> 00:03:31,294
Not right now.

68
00:03:31,378 --> 00:03:33,338
Will anybody help me?

69
00:03:34,464 --> 00:03:35,549
There's a little boy
who needs help.

70
00:03:35,632 --> 00:03:37,717
Please help me. I'm
sorry. Adults are talking.

71
00:03:37,801 --> 00:03:38,885
Run along.

72
00:03:41,430 --> 00:03:43,390
Charlotte! Don't.

73
00:03:45,016 --> 00:03:47,018
(BROODING MUSIC PLAYING)

74
00:03:48,728 --> 00:03:49,729
(BREATH TREMBLING)

75
00:03:50,564 --> 00:03:53,191
(SOMEONE WHISTLING
<i>TOREADOR SONG</i> IN DISTANCE)

76
00:04:00,031 --> 00:04:01,366
(DOOR CREAKING)

77
00:04:01,450 --> 00:04:03,452
(WATER RUNNING)

78
00:04:03,535 --> 00:04:04,953
(WHISTLING CONTINUES)

79
