96
00:05:31,414 --> 00:05:35,168
(CHARLOTTE BREATHING HEAVILY)
(HEART THUMPING)

97
00:05:35,252 --> 00:05:37,629
(MUFFLED, INDISTINCT CHATTER)

98
00:05:37,712 --> 00:05:40,799
(CHARLOTTE'S BREATH
TREMBLING)

99
00:05:50,600 --> 00:05:52,644
(SCREAMS)
