00:27:30,440 --> 00:27:32,818
This restaurant had
a lot of unique features.

503
00:27:33,485 --> 00:27:34,653
Like the marionette.

504
00:27:38,740 --> 00:27:39,825
You did your homework.

505
00:27:41,660 --> 00:27:42,661
Yeah.

506
00:27:43,245 --> 00:27:45,831
{\an8}The marionette truly
was one of a kind.

