00:27:46,415 --> 00:27:47,499
What's
"the marionette"?

508
00:27:48,375 --> 00:27:51,211
A marionette would come
out of this trapdoor on the stage

509
00:27:51,295 --> 00:27:52,546
and direct
the other animatronics

510
00:27:52,629 --> 00:27:54,131
during performances.
MICHAEL: That's right.

511
00:27:54,214 --> 00:27:55,924
Using a wireless signal.

512
00:27:56,466 --> 00:27:58,552
The technology was
<i>way</i> ahead of its time,

513
00:27:58,635 --> 00:28:01,263
but... they never made
another one.

